net.sourceforge.JDash.logger
Class LoggerPlaybackMonitor

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.JDash.ecu.comm.BaseMonitor
      net.sourceforge.JDash.logger.LoggerPlaybackMonitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable, ECUMonitor
public class LoggerPlaybackMonitor
extends BaseMonitor

This monitor is a completely different animal. It's designed to read it's values from an HSQLDB Database, re-submit them to the display subsystem that is listening. It's basically a facility to record, and playback ecu events. One more major difference between this monitor, and others is that this monitor is capable of both reading and writing to the database. This is basically a complete DAO class. Infact, this monitor is used for the data logging capabilities of this application.
